#: Game.Levels.FinsetOperations.L20_ComplementViaSdiff
msgid "# Double Set Difference and Complement\n"
"\n"
"Here's a useful identity that connects set difference to intersection:\n"
"\n"
"آ§0\n"
"\n"
"Read it aloud: 'removing from آ§1 everything that's in آ§2 but not in آ§3\n"
"leaves exactly the elements of آ§4 that *are* in آ§5.'\n"
"\n"
"This is the **complement principle**: if you think of آ§6 as a 'universe,'\n"
"then آ§7 is the 'complement of آ§8 within آ§9.' Taking the complement\n"
"again (آ§10) gets you back to آ§11 â€” the part of آ§12 inside\n"
"your universe.\n"
"\n"
"After آ§13 and rewriting with آ§14 (twice) and\n"
"آ§15, the goal becomes:\n"
"\n"
"آ§16\n"
"\n"
"The backward direction is straightforward: if آ§17, then\n"
"آ§18 is immediate, and آ§19 follows because آ§20\n"
