#: Game.Levels.BinomialTheorem.L10_DifferentSpecialization
msgid "Three rewrites inside آ§0: آ§1.\n"
"\n"
"**New move**: آ§2 inside a summand simplification. This is\n"
"needed whenever the target expression has factors in a different\n"
