"آ§4 is another. Their **componentwise sum** â€” adding\n"
"corresponding entries â€” should give آ§5:\n"
"\n"
"| Index | آ§6 | آ§7 | Sum |\n"
"|---|---|---|---|\n"
"| 0 | 1 | 2 | 3 |\n"
"| 1 | 0 | 3 | 3 |\n"
"\n"
"In Lean, componentwise sum is expressed as a function:\n"
"آ§8 â€” at each index آ§9, add the entries.\n"
"\n"
