"In plain mathematics, this is the obvious fact that elements of\n"
"آ§5 are just numbers, and two numbers are equal\n"
"when they're the same number. So why does Lean need a lemma for this?\n"
"\n"
"Because آ§6 is a **subtype** â€” a wrapper around a natural number\n"
"and a proof. An element آ§7 is really آ§8:\n"
