"the sum of the individual sizes. Equivalently:\n"
"\n"
"آ§2\n"
"\n"
"(but the additive form avoids natural number subtraction issues).\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Given the sizes of آ§3, آ§4, and their intersection,\n"
"compute the size of their union."
