msgid "# Lists Can Have Duplicates\n"
"\n"
"Before we move to permutations, let's observe something important:\n"
"**lists can contain duplicate elements**.\n"
"\n"
"Consider a list آ§0 where element آ§1 already appears (آ§2).\n"
"If you prepend آ§3 to آ§4 with آ§5, the resulting list has\n"
"آ§6 appearing at least twice â€” once at the head, and at least once\n"
"in the tail.\n"
"\n"
"This is a preview of the abstraction ladder:\n"
