"| **Multiset** | yes | آ§8 counts all entries |\n"
"| **Finset** | no | آ§9 counts distinct elements |\n"
"\n"
"Lists and multisets keep every copy. Finsets discard duplicates,\n"
"so their آ§10 can be strictly smaller than the list آ§11.\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Given a list آ§12 of length 1 and an element آ§13\n"
"that belongs to آ§14, compute the length of آ§15.\n"
"\n"
"Since آ§16, the list آ§17 contains آ§18 at least twice.\n"
"But آ§19 counts all entries â€” duplicates included. You'll peel\n"
