"  a permutation: آ§7\n"
"- **آ§8** â€” if آ§9, then آ§10\n"
"  (prepending the same element preserves the permutation)\n"
"- **آ§11** â€” if آ§12 and آ§13,\n"
"  then آ§14 (chain permutations)\n"
"\n"
"**Your task**: Prove that آ§15 is a permutation of آ§16.\n"
"This is a single swap of the first two elements."
