#: Game.Levels.BigOpIntro.L15_Boss
msgid "Congratulations! You've mastered the Big Operators Introduction.\n"
"\n"
"You can now:\n"
"- **Compute** sums and products by peeling with\n"
"  آ§0/آ§1 and closing with\n"
"  آ§2/آ§3\n"
"- **Simplify** summands/factors pointwise with آ§4/آ§5\n"
"- **Connect** cardinality to summation via آ§6\n"
"- **Distinguish** the base cases: empty sum = 0, empty product = 1\n"
"\n"
"The complete toolkit:\n"
"\n"
"| Lemma | What it does |\n"
"|-------|-------------|\n"
"| آ§7 / آ§8 | Empty sum = 0, empty product = 1 |\n"
"| آ§9 / آ§10 | Singleton = function value |\n"
"| آ§11 / آ§12 | Peel one element (needs آ§13) |\n"
"| آ§14 / آ§15 | Rewrite the summand/factor pointwise |\n"
"| آ§16 | Cardinality = sum of 1 |\n"
"\n"
"**Looking ahead**: The next world introduces algebraic manipulation\n"
"of big operators. A key tool will be آ§17, which\n"
"unfolds sums over آ§18 one element at a time:\n"
"\n"
"آ§19\n"
"\n"
"This is the **split-off-the-last-term** strategy: to evaluate or prove\n"
"something about a sum over آ§20, split off the last term and\n"
