msgid "The **general pigeonhole principle**: for ANY آ§0, no injective\n"
"function from آ§1 to آ§2 exists.\n"
"\n"
"The proof was *identical* to Level 21 â€” the same three steps,\n"
"the same lemmas. The numbers changed from آ§3 and آ§4 to آ§5\n"
"and آ§6, but آ§7 handles the arithmetic in both cases.\n"
"\n"
"This is the power of the cardinality approach: the proof doesn't\n"
"depend on the specific sizes. The PsetFin approach (exhaustive\n"
