msgid "# Pigeonhole Without Case Analysis\n"
"\n"
"In PsetFin, you proved the pigeonhole principle for آ§0\n"
"by exhaustive case analysis â€” 6 branches, each checked by hand.\n"
"The conclusion promised: 'cardinality tools prove pigeonhole for\n"
"any n in a few lines.' Time to deliver.\n"
"\n"
"The cardinality argument is beautifully simple:\n"
"\n"
"1. If آ§1 were injective, then by\n"
"   آ§2, the image of ALL آ§3 elements\n"
"   under آ§4 would have آ§5 elements.\n"
"\n"
"2. But the image lives inside آ§6, which only has آ§7 elements.\n"
"   By آ§8 + آ§9, the image has\n"
"   at most آ§10 elements.\n"
"\n"
"3. So آ§11 â€” contradiction.\n"
"\n"
"No case analysis. No classifying outputs. Just counting.\n"
"\n"
"All three tools were introduced in the previous two levels:\n"
"آ§12, آ§13, آ§14, and آ§15. Now you\n"
"combine them with آ§16 and آ§17 for\n"
"the full pigeonhole argument."
