msgid "# Why Finiteness Matters\n"
"\n"
"You've now learned all five composition rules:\n"
"\n"
"| Construction | Formula | Lemma |\n"
"|---|---|---|\n"
"| آ§0 | آ§1 | آ§2 |\n"
"| آ§3 | آ§4 | آ§5 |\n"
