"with a آ§15 instance.\n"
"\n"
"Consider the natural numbers آ§16. There are infinitely many functions\n"
"آ§17 (for each natural number, independently choose آ§18 or\n"
"آ§19). The \"formula\" آ§20 is meaningless because آ§21\n"
"is undefined â€” آ§22 has no آ§23 instance. Writing آ§24\n"
"in Lean is a type error.\n"
"\n"
