msgid "# Powerset: All Subsets of a Set\n"
"\n"
"Given a finite set آ§0, how many subsets does it have? What if you only\n"
"want subsets of a specific size?\n"
"\n"
"**Concrete motivation**: Imagine choosing toppings for a pizza from a\n"
"menu of آ§1 items. Each topping is independently *in* or *out* â€” that\n"
"gives آ§2 possible pizzas. If you want exactly آ§3 toppings, there\n"
"are آ§4 options. The powerset formalizes this: it is the\n"
"collection of all possible choices.\n"
"\n"
"The **powerset** آ§5 is the collection of all subsets of آ§6.\n"
"The key characterization: آ§7 if and only if آ§8.\n"
"\n"
"In this world you'll learn:\n"
"\n"
